Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方運輸艦從環後側出現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 開始狙擊炮戰
