Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種速度 是無人艦的自殺性攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自 自殺性攻擊 怎麼會 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
