Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回來 阿勒路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲汀娜·塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員生還
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾德說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要生還
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支持住 無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認敵方MS部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在運輸艦背後了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人總數 36架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入死角了
