Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在引誘我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貿然上前的話會城池不保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人也是強弩之末了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的攻擊 GN field能支撐住的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 菲爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下 再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會被MS威脅到艦船的遠距離攻擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣  原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人革聯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 瑟爾蓋·史米盧做夫這次的作戰目標不是托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是俘獲Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的預測失誤了？ 怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經發過誓不會再犯錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機雷群 遭到埋伏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑這種程度就想把Kyrios…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這刺痛般的感覺是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和當時一樣的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底 是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落入陷阱的「天人」
